 MBOMBELA – Hoërskool Bergvlam’s production is based on the beloved Cats by Andrew Lloyd Webber and promises breathtaking singing and dancing to warm the heart. Tickets are available from the school’s administration office throughout the day and each night at the door at R80 per adult and R50 for children. However, this afternoon they are having a happy hour on ticket sales for Catz Unlimited between 13:00 and 15:00. ALSO SEE: VIDEO: Listen to Johnny Clegg They will be selling for half price, so make your way to the school without delay.  Tomorrow night’s gala event costs R100 per person. Catz Unlimited starts at 18:00 at Hoërskool Bergvlam. ALSO READ: Mbombelan team looking for its time in the sun at solar challenge